dialogue.name: mc
dialogue.string: "Wow, that was a lot more fun than I thought. Didn't do half bad myself, I think."

dialogue.name: monika
dialogue.string: "You were really holding out on us this long, hmm? We've been trying to get you to join us for ages!"

dialogue.name: mc
dialogue.string: "How long have you guys been here?!"

dialogue.name: natsuki
dialogue.string: "Hahaha! We've been here for a while. I can't believe you were so into it that you didn't notice."

dialogue.name: yuri
dialogue.string: "Your singing voice is just as naturally confident as your poem reading voice."

dialogue.name: bf
dialogue.string: (Translation) What did I tell you, broski?

dialogue.name: mc
dialogue.string: (There's no way that actually worked, right..?)
